title: may 12: Susie Maroney takes a nice long swim
description:
Today on 365 with mxmtoon, Maia talks about Susie Maroney, an Australian marathon swimmer who became the first person to swim from Cuba to Florida, an impressive distance of over 100 miles that she covered in only 24 hours and 31 minutes. Then, Maia talks about Harry Styles’s first solo album. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
